      {
        "text": "6 months delivers auth and payments as independent services, eliminating incident scenario and reducing PCI scope",
        "truth": 0.85,
        "indeterminacy": 0.12,
        "falsity": 0.03
      },
      {
        "text": "Audit pipeline is the actual critical path bottleneck, not code delivery",
